dialogues.Grady:
[1]August Rosenbluth...Lord and Master of the Known and Unknown Universes. Ringmaster Extraordinaire. Jacob looks baffled. Camel laughs as he drinks more; 
[2]Stand inside the tent and smack the sides with this when you see a head trying to peek in without paying. Jacob follows Grady into the tent... 
[3]It's OK Camel. Tomorrow's payday. We'll get you some moonshine.
